<hr><br>
<center>

In the <a style="text-decoration:none; color: silver" href="https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/gamecorner">PS! Game Corner</a> chat room, users can put their favourite Pok√©mon and characters together on digital canvases to express their personality and style to the community. Under normal circumstances, these canvases only get displayed in the room when certain conditions are met, such as when someone wins a game. 

<br><br>The goal of the gallery is to exhibit users' canvases in a place where they can be viewed and appreciated by anyone at any time.

